Key Match Events: Rassie van der Dussen scored 133 runs for South Africa
Quinton de Kock scored 114 runs for South Africa
South Africa scored 357/4, their highest score against New Zealand in ODIs
Post-Match Reflections: Rassie van der Dussen was named Player of the Match
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played under lights at the Maharashtra Cricket Association Stadium in Pune
Others: The match was the 32nd of the ICC Cricket World Cup 2023-24, and South Africa won by 190 runs
